attr.title: Going Home Revisited
attr.desc: Going Home Revisited is an atmospheric, narrative-driven game where players explore a beautifully rendered, nostalgic world. As you journey through the protagonist's memories, uncovering personal stories and hidden secrets, you'll be immersed in a poignant tale of reflection and discovery. With its evocative visuals and compelling storytelling, it offers a deeply emotional gaming experience.
attr.inst: All files are included. Kindly consider supporting the dev by purchasing the game https://flamendless.itch.io/going-home-revisited
